org.apache.wml

Interface WMLMetaElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.w3c.dom.Element, org.w3c.dom.Node, WMLElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WMLMetaElementImpl

    public interface WMLMetaElement
extends WMLElement

    The interface is modeled after DOM1 Spec for HTML from W3C. The DTD used in this DOM model is from http://www.wapforum.org/DTD/wml_1.1.xml

    The meta element contains meta-info of an WML deck (Section 11.3.2, WAP WML Version 16-Jun-1999)

    Version:
    $Id: WMLMetaElement.java 447258 2006-09-18 05:41:23Z mrglavas $
    Author:
    David Li
